Herbert Prior https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbert_Prior 0 Herbert Prior (2 July 1867 – 3 October 1954) was an English silent film actor. He appeared in 268 films between 1908 and 1934. He was born in Oxford, Oxfordshire, and died in Los Angeles, California. Herbert Prior ( 2_July_1867 – 3_October_1954 ) was an_English_silent_film_actor .
